{
  "stem": "8361.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we-- we could leave for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poland.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Poland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before 1918, it was Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born a Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'18 became Poland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So at that time, was Poland until '39.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really much, it was the same as really before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was anti-Semitism, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were used to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time we had-- yes, until '39.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1941.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39 The Soviet Union came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they weren't threatened, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just we had obey what they wanted us to do, that's all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't have a store.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have a store.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I closed the store right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When they came in, we closed it, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in 19--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, my husband went to work for the Soviet Union, you know, whatever they gave him work, and he worked.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was with my baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had my baby already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, I didn't. '40 he was born.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because in Soviet Union you can't have business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would send you to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We couldn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you are smart enough and closed it, you're clean.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, they would send you to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because you can't have business in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, we had to stand in line for bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't get anything--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, 1939.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we could still survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no Nazis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So it was OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How we get-- we still knew people that had the-- the food like flour.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we traded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had our things we traded to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the most important thing, if you had to get something, you had to stay in line.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were a few stores, which were government stores, the Soviet Union stores.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stayed in line and got it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
